DataElement.preferredName: Statistics Analysis Plan Version Change Summary Text ISO21090.ED.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: Textual or media-based summary of the changes. EXAMPLE(S): (1) Distribution assumptions for some analyses were not met, so additional analyses were performed to check robustness of results. (2) Another drug in the class has been approved so additional analyses of a new exploratory endpoint have been added. (3) Site was non-compliant so additional analyses are needed to handle this site's data.
